24008","overview":"살인 훈련을 받은 젊은 킬러가 무자비한 범죄 조직으로부터 한 소년을 구출하려 한다. 소년만 구할 수 있다면 멘토를 등지는 것은 물론, 그 길을 가로막는 누구라도 제거할 것이다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"นักฆ่าเงาล่าทรชน","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/th/title/81624008","overview":"นักฆ่าสาวผู้มีทักษะในศาสตร์การสังหาร ท้าทายอำนาจของผู้ฝึกฝนเธอมาเพื่อช่วยเด็กชายคนหนึ่งจากองค์กรอาชญากรรมสุดโหดเหี้ยม และเธอจะไม่ไว้หน้าทุกคนที่ขวางทาง"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Відступна тінь","runtime":145,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ua/title/81624008","overview":"Майстерна молода вбивця порушує наказ свого наставника, щоб урятувати хлопчика від безжального злочинного синдикату, і готова знищити будь-кого, хто стане на її шляху."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Através das Sombras","runtime":143,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/br/title/81624008","overview":"Uma jovem assassina habilidosa desafia sua mentora para salvar um garoto de um terrível grupo criminoso. E ela vai destruir quem cruzar seu caminho."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"ロスト・イン・シャドー","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/jp/title/81624008","overview":"凄腕の若き殺し屋が、ひとりの少年を非情な犯罪組織から救うため、自らの師に背を向けて立ち上がる。そして、その行く手を阻む者を片っ端から滅ぼしていく。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/id/title/81624008","overview":"Si pembunuh belia yang terampil menentang mentornya demi menyelamatkan bocah lelaki dari sindikat kejahatan kejam. Ia akan menghancurkan siapa pun yang menghalanginya."},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"叛影浪客","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"在差点搞砸一次任务后，代号 13 的天才杀手被暂停执行其他任务。这名杀手少年遇到了一个名叫蒙吉的小男孩，他的母亲被一个犯罪集团杀害。当蒙吉失踪后，13 开始走上毁灭之路，寻找她唯一的朋友，甚至不惜违抗导师和自己所属的组织“影”。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Codename 13","runtime":144,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/de/title/81624008","overview":"Eine junge Attentäterin widersetzt sich ihrem Mentor, um einen Jungen vor einem skrupellosen Verbrechersyndikat zu retten — und niemand kann sich ihr in den Weg stellen."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Błędny cień","runtime":145,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/pl/title/81624008","overview":"Biegła w sztuce zabijania młoda zabójczyni rzuca wyzwanie swojemu mentorowi, aby uratować chłopca przed potężnym syndykatem. Zniszczy każdego, kto stanie jej na drodze."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Kóbor árnyék","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hu/title/81624008","overview":"A gyilkolás művészetében jártas fiatal bérgyilkos szembeszáll a mentorával, hogy megmentsen egy kisfiút egy kegyetlen bűnszervezettől – és mindenkit megsemmisít, aki az útjába áll."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"De Schaduw Verdwaalt","runtime":145,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/nl/title/81624008","overview":"Een getalenteerde jonge huurmoordenaar trotseert haar mentor en redt een jongen van een meedogenloos misdaadsyndicaat, klaar om iedereen op haar pad te vernietigen."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/it/title/81624008","overview":"Una giovane e abile assassina sfida chi le ha fatto da mentore per salvare un ragazzino da una spietata organizzazione criminale... ed eliminerà chiunque la ostacoli."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Ze stínů","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/cz/title/81624008","overview":"Mladá, ale zkušená nájemná vražedkyně se vzepře svému mentorovi, aby zachránila kluka před krutým zločineckým gangem. A zlikviduje každého, kdo by jí stál v cestě."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Asi 13","runtime":145,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/tr/title/81624008","overview":"Öldürme sanatında çok yetenekli olan genç bir suikastçı, bir çocuğu zalim bir suç örgütünden kurtarmak için akıl hocasına meydan okur ve yoluna çıkan hiç kimseye acımaz."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Fuera de las sombras","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/mx/title/81624008","overview":"Una joven sicaria, experta en el arte de matar, desafía a su mentora para salvar a un niño de una organización criminal... sin tener piedad de quien se cruce en su camino."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Fuera de las sombras","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/es/title/81624008","overview":"Una joven asesina experta en el arte de matar se enfrenta a su mentora para salvar a un niño de una despiadada banda criminal... y destruirá a cualquiera que se cruce en su camino."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Η Αδέσποτη των Σκιών","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/gr/title/81624008","overview":"Μια νεαρή ειδικευμένη δολοφόνος αψηφά τον μέντορά της για να σώσει ένα αγόρι από ένα αδίστακτο εγκληματικό συνδικάτο – και θα καταστρέψει τους πάντες στο διάβα της."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Nume de cod 13","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ro/title/81624008","overview":"Versată în arta uciderii, o tânără asasină îl sfidează pe mentorul ei pentru a salva un băiat de un sindicat nemilos al crimei. Și va distruge pe oricine îi stă în cale."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":144,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/dk/title/81624008","overview":"En ung, dygtig snigmorder trodser sin mentor for at redde en dreng fra hensynsløse forbrydere – og ødelægger alt, der kommer i vejen."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"叛影浪客","runtime":144,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/tw/title/81624008","overview":"在差點搞砸一次任務後，代號13的天才殺手被暫停執行其他任務。 這名殺手少年遇到了一個名叫蒙吉的小男孩，他的母親被一個犯罪集團殺害。 當蒙吉失踪後，13開始走上毀滅之路，尋找她唯一的朋友，甚至不惜違抗導師和自己所屬的組織“影”。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"מתוך הצללים","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/il/title/81624008","overview":"מתנקשת צעירה ומיומנת פועלת בניגוד לרצונו של המנטור שלה ויוצאת להציל ילד מציפורניו של סינדיקט פשע אכזרי. והיא מתכוונת לחסל כל מי שיעמוד בדרכה."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Выйти из тени","runtime":144,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ru/title/81624008","overview":"Молодая киллерша, только начинающая работать в секретной организации наёмных убийц «Тени», неудачно проявляет себя на первом задании и получает приказ залечь на дно в Джакарте. Ожидая дальнейших инструкций, она живёт в бедном районе и проникается симпатией к соседскому мальчишке, который остаётся сиротой. Когда мальчик внезапно исчезает, девушка отправляется на его поиски, что приводит её в самое сердце криминального мира Джакарты."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Sát thủ mật danh 13","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/vn/title/81624008","overview":"Có kỹ năng giết người điêu luyện, sát thủ trẻ nọ bất tuân lời thầy để cứu một cậu bé khỏi một tổ chức tội phạm tàn nhẫn... và cô sẽ tiêu diệt bất cứ ai cản đường."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"سایه‌گردها","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"یک آدمکش جوان، با سرپیچی از مربی و سازمانش، مصمم است پسری را که مادرش را در چنگال یک سازمان تبهکار جنایی قدرتمند از دست داده نجات دهد."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"Perdida na Sombra","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/pt/title/81624008","overview":"Uma jovem assassina versada na arte de matar desafia a sua mentora para salvar um rapaz de uma organização criminosa... e vai destruir quem se atravessar no seu caminho."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"المتمردة الشاردة","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ae/title/81624008","overview":"تتمتع قاتلة مأجورة شابة بمهارة فن القتل، فتتحدى مرشدتها لإنقاذ صبي من منظمة إجرامية قاسية لا تعرف الرحمة... عازمة على تدمير أي شخص في طريقها."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"AE","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"المتمردة الشاردة","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/sa/title/81624008","overview":"تتمتع قاتلة مأجورة شابة بمهارة فن القتل، فتتحدى مرشدتها لإنقاذ صبي من منظمة إجرامية قاسية لا تعرف الرحمة... عازمة على تدمير أي شخص في طريقها."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"叛影浪客","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hk/title/81624008","overview":"手段高明的年輕殺手違背師父的命令，執意從殺人不眨眼的犯罪集團手中拯救一個小男孩，擋她去路者只有死路一條。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"叛影浪客","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/sg-zh/title/81624008","overview":"为了从冷酷无情的犯罪集团手中救出一个男孩，这名杀人手法高超的年轻刺客不仅违抗导师的命令，还将除掉挡在她面前的任何阻碍。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"SG","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Lutalice iz Sjena","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hr/title/81624008","overview":"Djevojka ubojica vješta u svome poslu suprotstavi se svome mentoru kako bi dječaka spasila od nemilosrdne kriminalne skupine i pritom će uništiti sve pred sobom."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/fi/title/81624008","overview":"Nuori ja taitava salamurhaaja uhmaa mentoriaan pelastaakseen armottoman rikossyndikaatin käsiin joutuneen pojan ja on valmis tuhoamaan jokaisen, joka astuu hänen tielleen."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"L'Ombre rebelle","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ca-fr/title/81624008","overview":"Une jeune assassine douée défie son mentor pour sauver un garçon menacé par une organisation criminelle impitoyable, détruisant tous ceux qui se dressent sur son chemin."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"द शैडो स्ट्रेज़","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/in-hi/title/81624008","overview":"जान लेने की कला में माहिर एक जवान कातिल, अपने गुरु की मर्ज़ी के खिलाफ़ एक लड़के को बेरहम क्राइम सिंडिकेट से बचाती है - और वह अपने रास्ते में आने वाले किसी भी शख्स को नहीं बख्शेगी."},"name":"हिन्दी","iso_639_1":"hi","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Hindi"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/my/title/81624008","overview":"Seorang pembunuh muda yang cekap menentang mentornya demi menyelamatkan seorang budak lelaki daripada sindiket jenayah kejam sehingga sanggup menghapuskan sesiapa sahaja."},"name":"Bahasa melayu","iso_639_1":"ms","iso_3166_1":"MY","english_name":"Malay"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/no/title/81624008","overview":"En ung snikmorder trosser mentoren sin for å redde en gutt fra et nådeløst kriminelt nettverk – og hun kommer til å knuse alle som står i veien for henne."},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/se/title/81624008","overview":"En ung, skicklig lönnmördare trotsar sin mentor för att rädda en pojke från ett hänsynslöst brottssyndikat – och hon är redo att förgöra alla som står i hennes väg."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ph/title/81624008","overview":"Isang assassin na eksperto sa pagpatay ang sumuway sa mentor niya para iligtas ang isang batang lalaki mula sa sindikato—at patutumbahin niya ang hahadlang sa kanya."},"name":"","iso_639_1":"tl","iso_3166_1":"PH","english_name":"Tagalog"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"17-letna dobro izurjena morilka s kodnim imenom Agent 13 je suspendirana zaradi neuspešne misije na Japonskem. Spozna 11-letnega Monjija, ki je izgubil mamo, in da bi ga lahko rešila pred neusmiljeno kriminalno združbo, se upre svojemu mentorju ter uničila bo vsakogar, ki ji bo na poti."},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"},{"data":{"title":"Бездомни сенки","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"След като почти проваля мисия, 17-годишната убийца Кодово име 13 (Аурора Риберо) се оказа отстранена от по-нататъшни задължения. Тийнейджърката-убиец среща Монджи (Али Фикри) – младо момче, загубило майка си заради престъпен синдикат. Когато Монджи изчезва, 13 се отправя на унищожително пътешествие, за да намери единствения си приятел… дори с цената на това да се противопостави на наставника си и организацията, към която принадлежи – Сенките."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Z tieňov","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Mladá nájomná vrahyňa sa rozhodne zachrániť chlapca, ktorému zločinecký gang zabil matku. Musí sa preto ale postaviť svojmu mentorovi aj organizácii, pre ktorú pracuje."},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"მოხეტიალე ჩრდილი","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"მკვლელობის ხელოვნებაში გამოცდილი ახალგაზრდა ასასინი უპირისპირდება თავის მენტორს, რათა ბიჭი დაუნდობელი კრიმინალური სინდიკატისგან გადაარჩინოს - და ის გაანადგურებს ყველას, ვინც მას გზაზე გადაეღობება."},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"De Schaduw Verdwaalt","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"BE","english_name":"Dutch"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"672da0b8599da28980958b8e","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/672da0b8599da28980958b8e","author":"MovieGuys","content":"As is often the case with Indonesian action films, The Shadow Strays is exceptionally violent.\r\n\r\nImmediately, this will shut out a portion of viewers, who find the whole thing far too gratuitously bloody. \r\n\r\nThe story is the by now, well established, girl boss proposition. That said, everything is done so well, its actually quite watchable. Martial art fight scenes, gun play and more are beautifully choreographed and highly creative. \r\n\r\nActing is competent too, with very relatable main characters you come to sympathise with. \r\n\r\nIn summary, if you can get past the extreme violence, this is quite watchable.Take a look but only if you have a strong stomach.","created_at":"2024-11-08T05:25:12.460Z","updated_at":"2024-11-08T05:27:38.880Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":7,"username":"MovieGuys","avatar_path":null}}],"recommendations":[{"id":1154864,"adult":false,"title":"Cursed","video":false,"overview":"The lives of six girls belong to different worlds although connected to each other through a doll called Molly, whose existence dates back to 1976, when she appeared among the rubble of the great fire of the San Carlos orphanage, in northern Spain","genre_ids":[27,28,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.4166,"vote_count":41,"poster_path":"/nQlq8Dp0DiYbAmybZFwp2JvS2Ml.jpg","release_date":"2023-10-20","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":"/3bqfwYl2wZSHxLjnVaTgXoZKQ8M.jpg","original_title":"Malditas","original_language":"es"},{"id":1450219,"adult":false,"title":"Comme une abeille","video":false,"overview":"","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0071,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/7qnKukyS1t5vfVE5cNl2CbnJX40.jpg","release_date":"2025-03-01","vote_average":8.4,"backdrop_path":"/wT7OuI9VXKY9iyWmVtrVP2ZA5tl.jpg","original_title":"Comme une abeille","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1174188,"adult":false,"title":"It’s Okay!","video":false,"overview":"In-young, a high school student who is alone due to her parents' sudden death, is forced out because of her overdue rent and stays hidden in the Korean Dance Art Troupe where she belongs. In-young, who is still living bravely and brightly despite the sad situation, is caught by the director of the art troupe who is known for being rough, and the director who could not put In-young in the art troupe eventually begins to live with her.","genre_ids":[10751,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0903,"vote_count":11,"poster_path":"/dmgJPkwSQOzNWVaM2grAqQvP1AY.jpg","release_date":"2025-02-26","vote_average":7.136,"backdrop_path":"/xcsoHMxB73fSwAH1h07RA9u6Oec.jpg","original_title":"괜찮아 괜찮아 괜찮아!","original_language":"ko"},{"id":263132,"adult":false,"title":"Naked Ambition 3D","video":false,"overview":"An honors graduate in literature, Wyman is stuck writing cheap erotic fiction, but somehow ends up starring in an AV film. Suddenly a porn superstar in Japan, he discovers a whole new world fraught with pleasure, pain and more twists and turns than he or the audience expects.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.2095,"vote_count":47,"poster_path":"/5XMtLOARkGjttCbu6Hgmh6v0Mk4.jpg","release_date":"2014-03-25","vote_average":4.979,"backdrop_path":"/4TOIMcSs7qg67zaO9IHSqushUb5.jpg","original_title":"3D 豪情","original_language":"cn"},{"id":770684,"adult":false,"title":"The Retaliators","video":false,"overview":"An upstanding pastor uncovers a dark and twisted underworld as he searches for answers surrounding his daughter's brutal murder.","genre_ids":[27,53,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5515,"vote_count":71,"poster_path":"/vz4GSAFdKeLQUBoHNGynd716atQ.jpg","release_date":"2022-09-08","vote_average":5.711,"backdrop_path":"/mM2U4ZfXlOXS3KmpGT1zf3OHMuZ.jpg","original_title":"The Retaliators","original_language":"en"},{"id":1369595,"adult":false,"title":"The Other Side","video":false,"overview":"A forty-year-old poet wakes up handcuffed to a hospital bed. Accused of his mother's murder, he claims it was an act of love: a plan to aid his mother's death and end his own life at the same time.","genre_ids":[18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.261,"vote_count":28,"poster_path":"/axujDwRWO7K5HSvzvLfZoXbeVbh.jpg","release_date":"2024-10-25","vote_average":8.4,"backdrop_path":"/nycI0r92qCelKsEF7OCf4qHFwyy.jpg","original_title":"Del otro lado del jardín","original_language":"es"},{"id":1143508,"adult":false,"title":"You Gotta Believe","video":false,"overview":"After dedicating the season to a teammate’s ailing father, a group of underestimated Ft. Worth youth baseball players takes its Cinderella run all the way to the 2002 Little League World Series—culminating in a record-breaking showdown that became an instant ESPN classic.","genre_ids":[10751,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8614,"vote_cou