,"release_date":"1995-08-05","vote_average":6.506,"backdrop_path":"/kZbLOAlCB3htkhyZzTkUv21i0gv.jpg","original_title":"The Prophecy","original_language":"en"},{"id":274626,"adult":false,"title":"Animal","video":false,"overview":"When plans for a weekend vacation hit a dead end, a group of close-knit friends find themselves stranded in unfamiliar territory, pursued by a menacing predator. Holed up in an isolated cabin, tensions mount as long-buried secrets are revealed. As the body count rises, the group must put their differences aside and fight for survival.","genre_ids":[53,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.9896,"vote_count":285,"poster_path":"/jAWZHSV5C6EOPuG2zVG9fISO5tQ.jpg","release_date":"2014-06-17","vote_average":5.116,"backdrop_path":"/flgJZkK8j7QG98t2NwOM7TlbBmK.jpg","original_title":"Animal","original_language":"en"},{"id":1154223,"adult":false,"title":"Hunting with Tigers","video":false,"overview":"Malik, a young Parisian hustler, discovers that his stepfather Serge, a famous bank robber, has been arrested along with his accomplices. During the trial, Iris, one of the accused's lawyers, Chérif, requests Malik to accept a dangerous heist in exchange for Serge and her client's liberty. Malik must convince and reunite Chérif's former partners to accomplish this high-risk stickup.","genre_ids":[28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.628,"vote_count":103,"poster_path":"/lw6ovFjd6fhq6SEklcxP5axlVJn.jpg","release_date":"2024-11-22","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":"/gKDFHQsEdnwZW0RC0htr0aYYH5W.jpg","original_title":"Tigres et Hyènes","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1025491,"adult":false,"title":"Freud's Last Session","video":false,"overview":"On the eve of the Second World War, two of the greatest minds of the twentieth century, C.S. Lewis and Sigmund Freud converge for their own personal battle over the existence of God. The film interweaves the lives of Freud and Lewis, past, present, and through fantasy, bursting from the confines of Freud’s study on a dynamic journey.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3038,"vote_count":164,"poster_path":"/mp7IBxFuvNZSVOOGESybvaPxd7y.jpg","release_date":"2023-12-22","vote_average":6.637,"backdrop_path":"/pg01mUOLX6bmkmQyQownrPDXbm.jpg","original_title":"Freud's Last Session","original_language":"en"},{"id":407375,"adult":false,"title":"Sniper: Ghost Shooter","video":false,"overview":"Elite snipers Brandon Beckett and Richard Miller are fighting extremists in the Middle East when the Colonel gives them a new mission: to protect a gas pipeline stretching from the Republic of Georgia to Western Europe from extremists eager to make a political statement. But when skirmishes with the enemy lead to U.S. snipers being killed by a ghost shooter who locks into their exact location, a security breach is suspected. Fingers are pointed and battle lines are drawn, all leading up to an explosive climax.","genre_ids":[28,18,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.8079,"vote_count":281,"poster_path":"/92YFviTZnjA6rj2jADoA2gmsjsz.jpg","release_date":"2016-08-02","vote_average":6.297,"backdrop_path":"/kgjg3FaCgv37ivD9g7v9d02Ap7J.jpg","original_title":"Sniper: Ghost Shooter","original_language":"en"},{"id":959092,"adult":false,"title":"Mayhem!","video":false,"overview":"Sam is a professional boxer about to get released from prison. While on parole, his past catches up with him and he has no choice but to flee. Five years later, he has rebuilt a simple life on an exotic island in Thailand with his wife and her daughter, but when he gets blackmailed by a dangerous local godfather, he must embark on a dangerous drug smuggling mission which results in a tragedy. Now he has only one purpose: to seek merciless vengeance.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.9099,"vote_count":210,"poster_path":"/u9035lysUz3ccloQt0SeIp1Mu8a.jpg","release_date":"2023-06-28","vote_average":6.683,"backdrop_path":"/dSbHiA9m62FhQxiSZoJmhzKlmZD.jpg","original_title":"Farang","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1088166,"adult":false,"title":"Relay","video":false,"overview":"A broker of lucrative payoffs between corrupt corporations and the individuals who threaten them breaks his own rules when a new client seeks his protection to stay alive.","genre_ids":[28,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.5662,"vote_count":330,"poster_path":"/mpwccO2L8LUVtVTJTdgUVgoQqAo.jpg","release_date":"2025-08-21","vote_average":6.95,"backdrop_path":"/9knXxeYDmxgYi7cmoQzCisP3b6w.jpg","original_title":"Relay","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":59,"adult":false,"title":"A History of Violence","video":false,"overview":"An average family is thrust into the spotlight after the father commits a seemingly self-defense murder at his diner.","genre_ids":[18,53,80],"popularity":2.9401,"vote_count":3617,"poster_path":"/3qnO72NHmUgs9JZXAmu4aId9QDl.jpg","release_date":"2005-09-23","vote_average":7.164,"backdrop_path":"/iZHJsUYxhjI6kbooHoQRWXv6F8E.jpg","original_title":"A History of Violence","original_language":"en"},{"id":77,"adult":false,"title":"Memento","video":false,"overview":"Leonard Shelby is tracking down the man who raped and murdered his wife. The difficulty of locating his wife's killer, however, is compounded by the fact that he suffers from a rare, untreatable form of short-term memory loss. Although he can recall details of life before his accident, Leonard cannot remember what happened fifteen minutes ago, where he's going, or why.","genre_ids":[9648,53],"popularity":9.0867,"vote_count":15928,"poster_path":"/fKTPH2WvH8nHTXeBYBVhawtRqtR.jpg","release_date":"2000-10-11","vote_average":8.176,"backdrop_path":"/7Wev9JMo6R5XAfz2KDvXb7oPMmy.jpg","original_title":"Memento","original_language":"en"},{"id":79,"adult":false,"title":"Hero","video":false,"overview":"During China's Warring States period, a district prefect arrives at the palace of Qin Shi Huang, claiming to have killed the three assassins who had made an attempt on the king's life three