mong love, friendship and the chance to rise within the mob.","genre_ids":[18,80],"popularity":2.5106,"vote_count":2256,"poster_path":"/9msfwOeGc9uL1iRRTBdEf15XonC.jpg","release_date":"1973-10-14","vote_average":7.057,"backdrop_path":"/qdecDSIVoqctIoYoOhLH3TgSYLD.jpg","original_title":"Mean Streets","original_language":"en"},{"id":242,"adult":false,"title":"The Godfather Part III","video":false,"overview":"In the midst of trying to legitimize his business dealings in 1979 New York and Italy, aging mafia don, Michael Corleone seeks forgiveness for his sins while taking a young protege under his wing.","genre_ids":[80,18,53],"popularity":9.5797,"vote_count":6717,"poster_path":"/lm3pQ2QoQ16pextRsmnUbG2onES.jpg","release_date":"1990-12-25","vote_average":7.418,"backdrop_path":"/8zhviPFJx25k8PbUOUL5sLOy9XE.jpg","original_title":"The Godfather Part III","original_language":"en"},{"id":246,"adult":false,"title":"Zatoichi","video":false,"overview":"Blind traveler Zatoichi is a master swordsman and a masseur with a fondness for gambling on dice games. When he arrives in a village torn apart by warring gangs, he sets out to protect the townspeople.","genre_ids":[12,18,28],"popularity":1.4296,"vote_count":934,"poster_path":"/iCIycswWbX1EDS6PYYBcR9ohrC.jpg","release_date":"2003-09-06","vote_average":7.239,"backdrop_path":"/kP6WiYHQUUXo6ZaXI06enkMsxkF.jpg","original_title":"座頭市","original_language":"ja"},{"id":247,"adult":false,"title":"The Killing","video":false,"overview":"Career criminal Johnny Clay recruits a sharpshooter, a crooked police officer, a bartender and a betting teller named George, among others, for one last job before he goes straight and gets married. But when George tells his restless wife about the scheme to steal millions from the racetrack where he works, she hatches a plot of her own.","genre_ids":[80,53],"popularity":1.7449,"vote_count":1680,"poster_path":"/A6VzUPcADZGYdGHlVdWvpMNDF5d.jpg","release_date":"1956-06-06","vote_average":7.646,"backdrop_path":"/2EltoldCMsYmP2BXJVGiuNalEWv.jpg","original_title":"The Killing","original_language":"en"},{"id":101,"adult":false,"title":"Léon: The Professional","video":false,"overview":"Léon, the top hit man in New York, has earned a rep as an effective \"cleaner\". But when his next-door neighbors are wiped out by a loose-cannon DEA agent, he becomes the unwilling custodian of 12-year-old Mathilda. Before long, Mathilda's thoughts turn to revenge, and she considers following in Léon's footsteps.","genre_ids":[80,18,28],"popularity":13.1027,"vote_count":15811,"poster_path":"/bxB2q91nKYp8JNzqE7t7TWBVupB.jpg","release_date":"1994-09-14","vote_average":8.294,"backdrop_path":"/jRJrQ72VLyEnVsvwfep8Xjlvu8c.jpg","original_title":"Léon","original_language":"fr"},{"id":103,"adult":false,"title":"Taxi Driver","video":false,"overview":"Suffering from insomnia, disturbed loner Travis Bickle takes a job as a New York City cabbie, haunting the streets nightly, growing increasingly detached from reality as he dreams of cleaning up the filthy city.","genre_ids":[80,18],"popularity":13.4122,"vote_count":13213,"poster_path":"/ekstpH614fwDX8DUln1a2Opz0N8.jpg","release_date":"1976-02-09","vote_average":8.127,"backdrop_path":"/9uddYYTNcLWpzUkl5iw1RUYhLhY.jpg","original_title":"Taxi Driver","original_language":"en"},{"id":107,"adult":false,"title":"Snatch","video":false,"overview":"Unscrupulous boxing promoters, violent bookies, a Russian gangster, incompetent amateur robbers, and supposedly Jewish jewellers fight to track down a priceless stolen diamond.","genre_ids":[80,35],"popularity":8.4587,"vote_count":9772,"poster_path":"/kJZoAHq1SLDdWjeNGtlHAnGpmFV.jpg","release_date":"2000-09-01","vote_average":7.816,"backdrop_path":"/gTghF8ardwJ48XLHkiapWk3ZmSo.jpg","original_title":"Snatch","original_language":"en"},{"id":1252551,"adult":false,"title":"Marni: The Story of Wewe Gombel","video":false,"overview":"After moving her family to a remote village, a busy single mother loses her son, who seems to have been abducted by a vengeful spirit.","genre_ids":[28,27,53],"popularity":0.2509,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/pIoqGkcroogisQBDe8Xo9QNfARK.jpg","release_date":"2024-06-27","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/gD7RKTTWMAb5sQzsMZYow4Lfg0f.jpg","original_title":"Marni: The Story of Wewe Gombel","original_language":"id"},{"id":111,"adult":false,"title":"Scarface","video":false,"overview":"After getting a green card in exchange for assassinating a Cuban government official, Tony Montana stakes a claim on the drug trade in Miami. Viciously murdering anyone who stands in his way, Tony eventually becomes the biggest drug lord in the state, controlling nearly all the cocaine that comes through Miami. But increased pressure from the police, wars with Colombian drug cartels and his own drug-fueled paranoia serve to fuel the flames of his eventual downfall.","genre_ids":[28,80,18],"popularity":14.3789,"vote_count":12757,"poster_path":"/iQ5ztdjvteGeboxtmRdXEChJOHh.jpg","release_date":"1983-12-09","vote_average":8.155,"backdrop_path":"/1qM2BYNE11Viby8ImC9LC00DgDr.jpg","original_title":"Scarface","original_language":"en"},{"id":117,"adult":false,"title":"The Untouchables","video":false,"overview":"Elliot Ness, an ambitious prohibition agent, is determined to take down Al Capone. In order to achieve this goal, he forms a group given the nickname “The Untouchables”.","genre_ids":[80,36,53],"popularity":4.7947,"vote_count":6065,"poster_path":"/sfMVTmd5irneaZOmQVdB8gFlId3.jpg","release_date":"1987-06-03","vote_average":7.754,"backdrop_path":"/sF2REAiVUcN90lrMeLfmEuHJl4B.jpg","original_title":"The Untouchables","original_language":"en"},{"id":121,"adult":false,"title":"The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers","video":false,"overview":"Frodo Baggins and the other members of the Fellowship continue on their sacred quest to destroy the One Ring--but on separate paths. Their destinies lie at two towers--Orthanc Tower in Isengard, where the corrupt wizard Saruman awaits, and Sauron's fortress at Barad-dur, deep within the dark lands of Mordor. Frodo and Sam are trekking to Mordor to destroy the One Ring of Power while Gimli, Legolas and Aragorn search for the orc-captured Merry and Pippin. All along, nefarious wizard Saruman awaits the Fellowship members at the Orthanc Tower in Isengard.","genre_ids":[12,14,28],"popularity":17.7989,"vote_count":23477,"poster_path":"/5VTN0pR8gcqV3EPUHHfMGnJYN9L.jpg","release_date":"2002-12-18","vote_average":8.413,"backdrop_path":"/kWYfW2Re0rUDE6IHhy4CRuKWeFr.jpg","original_title":"The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers","original_language":"en"},{"id":272,"adult":false,"title":"Batman Begins","video":false,"overview":"Driven by tragedy, billionaire Bruce Wayne dedicates his life to uncovering and defeating the corruption that plagues his home, Gotham City.  Unable to work within the system, he instead creates a new identity, a symbol of fear for the criminal underworld - The Batman.","genre_ids":[18,80,28],"popularity":12.5976,"vote_count":22282,"poster_path":"/sPX89Td70IDDjVr85jdSBb4rWGr.jpg","release_date":"2005-06-10","vote_average":7.721,"backdrop_path":"/9IIBboV7MCT0bTxzXHmWK1Hq558.jpg","original_title":"Batman Begins","original_language":"en"},{"id":275,"adult":false,"title":"Fargo","video":false,"overview":"Jerry, a small-town Minnesota car salesman is bursting at the seams with debt... but he's got a plan. He's going to hire two thugs to kidnap his wife in a scheme to collect a hefty ransom from his wealthy father-in-law. It's going to be a snap and nobody's going to get hurt... until people start dying. Enter Police Chief Marge, a coffee-drinking, parka-wearing - and extremely pregnant - investigator who'll stop at nothing to get her man. And if you think her small-time investigative skills will give the crooks a run for their ransom... you betcha!","genre_ids":[80,18,53],"popularity":8.1869,"vote_count":8901,"poster_path":"/rt7cpEr1uP6RTZykBFhBTcRaKvG.jpg","release_date":"1996-03-08","vote_average":7.847,"b